    "Skin infections and other secondary bacterial infections can lead to serious disease or fatality in persons with HIV/AIDS who have compromised immune systems.",
    "A Frontiers in Pharmacology frontiersin.org \"cytokine storm,\" or a strong immunological reaction that harms the body, can be brought on by monkeypox (Johnston et al., 2015; Soheili et al., 2022).",
    "Divergences in virulence and pathogenicity among various clades arise from variations in their genetic composition and the evolutionary processes they undergo during interhuman transmission, alterations in ecosystems, interactions between humans and wildlife, and undetected circulation in wildlife across geographical territories.",
    "Additionally, more proficient viral strains may shape the evolving epidemiology of MPXV (Kumbhar and Agarwala, 2022).",
    "The virus has two clades, clade I and clade II, which include clades IIa and IIb, which transmit disease worldwide."
